window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Since William James discovered he’s a necromancer, the world has changed drastically. The unseen world has emerged into the open after the elves from Prime sent two billion soldiers, magicians, pleasure slaves, and farmers to Earth.</p> <p>Will and Darcie have found Jack, but will he survive? Will the Sigma virus be the end for humanity?</p> <p>Governments will disintegrate. Both humans and elves will die as they fight for ownership of Earth.</p> <p>Will’s and Aloïse’s efforts to protect their family, friends, and community grow to encompass international efforts to defeat Elven attempts at planetary domination and save those who would otherwise perish.</p> <p>What do you do when everything takes a fall?</p>"; 
